description:
It was in Antioch that the disciples were first called Christian. This name wasn’t chosen by themselves but it was a descriptive name given to them by others based on their lives and witness. Today over 2 billion people claim to be Christian. May we live our lives today give such a strong witness about Jesus that others cannot but help describe us this way!
